+- [x] FR-E83: Snapshot-free journals replay unchanged (backward compat). Test:
+      `lifecycle-replay_test.ts` (regression-locked; whole existing suite);
+      `journal-compaction_test.ts::FR-E83 snapshot-free journal replays unchanged`
+      (FR-E83). Evidence: `deno test -A --no-check src/state/`.
+- [x] FR-E83: A snapshot with `snapshot_version` greater than supported fails
+      replay with an error naming the journal path and version. Test:
+      `journal-compaction_test.ts::FR-E83 forward refusal on unsupported snapshot_version`
+      (FR-E83). Evidence: `deno test -A --no-check src/state/journal-compaction_test.ts`.
+- [x] FR-E83: Replay seeds from the LATEST valid snapshot and applies only
+      events after it; `snapshot + tail` replay state is byte-equal to replaying
+      the full original journal. Test:
+      `journal-compaction_test.ts::FR-E83 snapshot+tail replay equals full replay`
+      (FR-E83). Evidence: `deno test -A --no-check src/state/journal-compaction_test.ts`.
+- [x] FR-E83: Replay of a compacted journal does not parse pre-snapshot history
