+     (1) plan/replay → faultHook("replayed"); (2) write `journal.jsonl.tmp`
+     (one snapshot line, zero tail) → faultHook("tmp-written"); (3) `Deno.open`
+     + `.sync()` fsync → faultHook("tmp-fsynced"); (4) `Deno.copyFile` journal →
